descriptionHtml:
Save game: Strong & Fearsome Nord Huntress which shes about to Avenge Kadlak\'s Death after Silverhand Invasion On Jorrvaskr
Stats: Level 21 
Style: Huntress

How to install:
Extract and Copy the file into C:\\Documents and Settings\\My Documents\\My Games\\Skyrim\\Saves
and enter the game , Load the save Game & Have Fun
